===Band Squad===
She formed a band at the end of the collaboration event with DJMAX with [[Girls' Frontline: M950A|M950A]], [[Girls' Frontline: TMP|TMP]], [[Girls' Frontline: K2|K2]], [[Girls' Frontline: AEK-999]] and [[Girls' Frontline: Clear|El CLear]], and took the seat of the drummer. She is also dubbed "White Doll", poking at her being not adept at expresing her emotions.

